      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "GOT A RUSTLER (5) returned a better run last time, finishing in the money (22.59) at this track behind BELLY RUBS in a Grade 5. Got back and turned spotting a start but found the line impressively. Has a strong record from box 5, including two wins. Capable of going well again. PAW REYA (2) is a talented type and proved too strong last time to win by 0.8 lengths at this track in a handy 22.41 beating BELLY RUBS. Deserves serious consideration again. GAME OF PHONES (7) fast away and ran her rivals ragged to score by a space two back then hit the frame last time when second at this track (22.42) latest. Hard to knock her form from this box, unbeaten in two starts. Expected to be in the finish again. FIGURE OF SPEECH (8) is in the mix despite missing out at this track last time.",
